   &UR; MIRACLE' BABY BORN IN TREE AS MOZAMBIQUE FLOOD RAGES BELOW &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Rosita Pedro was born in a tree Wednesday as the brown
crocodile-infested floodwaters of Mozambique's Limpopo River
swirled around her and her terrified mother. In the midst of the
country's worst floods in living memory, with death and destruction
all around them, Rosita's safe delivery was a miracle. &QL;
