   TRAVEL
</P>
<P>
   SOUTHEAST U.S. TRAVEL PACKAGE FROM ATLANTA
</P>
<P>
   SOUTHEAST-INNS _ A really great inn is more than somewhere to
spend the night. It is a warm place where you are pampered and
fussed over _ in short, made to feel like a welcome guest. The inn
might be country cozy or elegantly upscale. Here are some old
favorites and new discoveries from recent travels around the
Southeast _ and a few we're dreaming of visiting. (Thrasher,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   Eds: Embargoed for Sunday, March 5.
</P>
<P>
