<P>
   FESTIVALS _ 10 great warm-weather festivals around the South,
including the New Orleans Jazz and Heritage Festival, the 24th
Annual Spoleto Festival USA in Charleston and Pensacola's 51st
Annual Fiesta of Five Flags. (Thrasher, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   Eds: Embargoed for Sunday, March 5.
</P>
<P>
   GETAWAY _ When the Atlanta-based National Fish and Wildlife
Foundation published its first Directory of Birding and Nature
Festivals in 1995, it listed about two dozen events. This year,
there are more than 200 listed nationwide. The growth, director
Peter Stangel says, mirrors growing interest in birding and nature.
We carry the directory's listings for the Southeast this year.
(Pousner, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
