really don't care about the identity of the planet. I'd just like
to know the identity of the alien being that is passing itself off
as director Mike Nichols. How else to explain the claim that a
top-shelf director like Nichols actually helmed the galactic-sized
disaster What Planet Are You From? One star or dog of the week.
(Schwan, Palm Beach Post). 13. MOVED
</P>
