</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-ATTACK (Jerusalem) _ Israeli police report killing three
Palestinians said to be members of Hamas caught preparing a bomb
attack and arrested a fourth. Police were seeking a fifth man
thought to have escaped. By William A. Orme Jr.
</P>
<P>
