</P>
<P>
   SAPIENS-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Homo Sapiens 1900'': Peter
Cohen, director; a documentary on Nazi Germany and Stalinist
Russia. Reviewed by Stephen Holden.
</P>
