   &QR;  Plant City, Fla. _ The Florida Strawberry Festival Thursday
through March 12 features arts and crafts, country singers,
entertainment, food, vendors, exhibits and everything strawberry.
813-752-9194 or www.flstrawberryfestival
</P>
<P>
   .com.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Daytona Beach, Fla. _ Bike Week Friday through March 12 is one
of the oldest and largest international motorcycle festivals in the
world, with races, expos and concerts held throughout the city.
1-800-854-1234 or www
</P>
<P>
   .officialbikeweek.com.
</P>
