<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-02 17:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4793 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-MONA-FILM-REVIEW-NYT &LR;      03-02 0722
