<P>
   MAINE-COMPUTERS (Undated) _ Maine Governor Angus King's proposal
to give students from the 7th grade up a portable computer comes
under fire. Critics say they're concerned about providing students
a safe and pleasant learning environment. By David Abel. 700 words.
