<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-02 20:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4990 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-CHRISTIAN-RIGHT-1     03-02 1116
