<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-02 20:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5025 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-OBIT-STILES-NYT &LR;      03-02 0872
