-- Courses being taught at area colleges mirror the breadth of
society's interests. David McMenamin teaches a course at Boston
College titled ``Person and Social Responsibility.'' ``They start
out thinking they're going to change the world, and they leave
realizing how much they've been changed by it,'' said McMenamin.
(Tom Landers/The Boston Globe)
