Thursday for Malcolm Ferguson - yet another unarmed man who died in
a confrontation with police. But Mayor Rudolph Giuliani cast the
case as starkly different, saying the victim had a history of drug
crimes. Thomas Huertas, a neighbor, stood Thursday on the stairwell
of the building where Malcolm Ferguson was killed Wednesday night
by a plainclothes officer, Louis Rivera. (Angel Franco/The New York
Times)
