Rocker arrived for spring training today and began the process of
patching up his strained relationship with his coaches and
teammates. Rocker met with his teammates for a half-hour today
after his suspension was reduced by baseball arbitrator Shyam Das
on Wednesday. Afterward, he addressed the media for three minutes,
reading a copy of his apology that ran in today's
Journal-Constitution. (Marlene Karas/Cox News Service)
</P>
