18-year-old involvement, Prime Minister Ehud Barak has set a
deadline of July to withdraw the troops in the context of a peace
agreement with Syria. Ori Rosenstein, 19, in the bunkroom of the
Israeli Army outpost at Dlaat, said, ``The sooner we leave, the
better.'' (Deborah Sontag/The New York Times)
